{"data":{"post":{"id":"cG9zdDoxMTYy","excerpt":"<p>“Almost a flagship” with a 108-megapixel camera. At a presentation in China, Xiaomi introduced the long-awaited Mi CC9 Pro &#8211; an improved version of Mi CC9. This is the second smartphone in the world (after Nokia 9 PureView ) with a 5-module main camera. The 6.47-inch AMOLED display is curved around the edges, supports HDR and has a resolution [&hellip;]</p>\n","content":"\n<p>“Almost a flagship” with a 108-megapixel camera.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At a presentation in China, Xiaomi introduced the long-awaited Mi CC9 Pro &#8211; an improved version of Mi CC9. This is the second smartphone in the world (after Nokia 9 PureView ) with a 5-module main camera.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><span class=\"wp-image-1164 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:50%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/b95e4/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 256w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/1779b/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 512w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1024w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/f9ceb/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/b95e4/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 256w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/1779b/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 512w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1024w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/f9ceb/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1179w\" src=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/b95e4/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 256w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/1779b/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 512w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1024w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/f9ceb/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1179w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/b95e4/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 256w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/1779b/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 512w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1024w,\n/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/f9ceb/MI-CC9-Display.jpg 1179w\" src=\"/static/9887967cd1ed8cebb1202fa0f64628bf/87945/MI-CC9-Display.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 6.47-inch AMOLED display is curved around the edges, supports HDR and has a resolution of 1080 x 2340 pixels.&nbsp;An optical fingerprint scanner is built into the display &#8211; it works correctly even if the finger is wet, and offers a wider scanning area.&nbsp;This is the first smartphone in the world with such a sensor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A 32-megapixel selfie camera was placed in the drop-shaped recess. But the star of the program is, of course, the main camera. It consists of five modules, of which three were taken out in a separate island: this is the main 108 megapixel manufactured by Samsung, a 5 megapixel TV with support for 5x optical and 50x hybrid zoom, and a 12-megapixel portrait lens.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><span class=\"wp-image-1163 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:768px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:50%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/8c831/MI-CC9-Camera.png 192w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/643d6/MI-CC9-Camera.png 384w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" srcSet=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/8c831/MI-CC9-Camera.png 192w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/643d6/MI-CC9-Camera.png 384w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png 768w\" src=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/8c831/MI-CC9-Camera.png 192w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/643d6/MI-CC9-Camera.png 384w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" srcset=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/8c831/MI-CC9-Camera.png 192w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/643d6/MI-CC9-Camera.png 384w,\n/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png 768w\" src=\"/static/cc9b44c3eb40fbbf09c9d10bb25de4e9/2d1ba/MI-CC9-Camera.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Separately, two more modules were placed: a super-wide 20 MP with a viewing angle of 117 °, and a macro lens of 2 MP. These five cameras are complemented by two LED flashes. In addition to shooting in high resolution, the Mi CC9 Pro also offers intelligent scene enhancement, super-night mode, and 4K shooting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The heart of the smartphone is the Snapdragon 730G processor &#8211; the less powerful flagship Snapdragon 855+, but still in the top segment among the manufacturer&#8217;s chips. The battery capacity is an impressive 5,260 mAh. Fortunately, the company added a fast charge of 30 watts, so from 0 to 100%, it charges in just 65 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><span class=\"wp-image-1166 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:994px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:50.200803212851405%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/10d36/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 249w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/23483/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 497w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 994w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px\" srcSet=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/10d36/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 249w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/23483/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 497w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 994w\" src=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/10d36/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 249w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/23483/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 497w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 994w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 994px) 100vw, 994px\" srcset=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/10d36/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 249w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/23483/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 497w,\n/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg 994w\" src=\"/static/567c82050e168f47b71e892a4af3f116/020a0/XIaomi-Mi-CC9-Pro-30W-Fast-Charging-e1572937384632_1572941633.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Out of the box, the Mi CC9 Pro runs on MIUI 11 powered by Android 9 Pie. The firmware includes Game Turbo 2.0 game mode and a powerful speaker that produces the sound &#8220;twice as loud as compared to the speakers of other smartphones.&#8221; The smartphone supports Bluetooth 5.0 but retained a 3.5 mm headphone jack.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On November 5, Xiaomi opens pre-orders; on sale in China, the smartphone will arrive on November 11 in three colors: black, green and pearl white.&nbsp;The cost of new items is as follows:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>6 GB + 128 GB &#8211; 2,799 yuan</li><li>8 GB + 128 GB &#8211; 3 099 yuan</li><li>8 GB + 256 GB &#8211; 3 499 yuan</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>It is expected that Mi Note 10, which will be presented in Spain tomorrow, November 6, will become the European analog of Mi CC9 Pro.</p>\n","title":"Xiaomi announced the Mi CC9 Pro. It has six cameras and a massive battery","date":"November 05, 2019","featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"","localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='200'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20200'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M129%2031c-3%202-2%204%208%2016%2017%2021%2021%2024%2025%2022%204-1%205-5%203-8l-26-30c-3-2-8-3-10%200m37%2044c-2%202-1%206%202%208%204%203%2010%202%2010-2%200-5-9-9-12-6'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":2,"src":"/static/af6faf93479c8d1dc71a92eddceda701/b2e72/mi-CC9.jpg","srcSet":"/static/af6faf93479c8d1dc71a92eddceda701/84d81/mi-CC9.jpg 250w,\n/static/af6faf93479c8d1dc71a92eddceda701/f0719/mi-CC9.jpg 500w,\n/static/af6faf93479c8d1dc71a92eddceda701/b2e72/mi-CC9.jpg 955w","sizes":"(max-width: 955px) 100vw, 955px"}}}}}},"previous":{"uri":"/amazon-aws-ubuntu-linux-ec2-virtual-machine-setup/","title":"How to setup Linux on Amazon AWS Virtual Machine (ec2)"},"next":{"uri":"/xiaomi-mi-watch-officially-presented-wear-os-and-two-days-of-battery-life/","title":"Xiaomi Mi Watch officially presented: Wear OS and two days of battery life"}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoxMTYy","previousPostId":"cG9zdDoxMTY5","nextPostId":"cG9zdDoxMTU1"}}